    <p data-aid="142073946" id="p147" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin: 0px 0px 0.889em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0.778em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--text-secondary, var(--grey40)); --height: 19.59375px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 昼食と夕食（合計2時間以内）</p>
    <p data-aid="142073948" id="p149" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin: 0px 0px 0.889em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0.778em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--text-secondary, var(--grey40)); --height: 58.78125px;">午後9：00&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 教える約束がないかぎりアパートに戻る。教える約束がある場合は午後9時半までにアパートに戻る。</p>
    <p data-aid="142073950" id="p151" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin: 0px 0px 0.889em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0.778em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--text-secondary, var(--grey40)); --height: 19.59375px;">午後9：00－9：30&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 日記を書き，就寝の準備をし，祈る。</p>
    <p data-aid="142073952" id="p153" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; margin: 0px 0px 0.889em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 0.778em; line-height: 1.4; font-family: &quot;Ensign:Sans&quot;, Zoram, &quot;Zoram ldsLat&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: var(--text-secondary, var(--grey40)); --height: 19.59375px;">午後9:30－10:30&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 就寝</p>
